room_title: Escape room "Storm Surge" by Mind Trap Escape Rooms in Chicago
room_description: Loaded with almost a thousand tons of cargo, your on a vessel set sail from Chicago bound for Holland. Under the command of a 24-year-old captain, thick fog and storm surge conditions blinded the 13-man crew and your ship ran aground some 300 feet off of South Manitou Island. You have 1 hour to escape the ship before it fully capsizes.
